This file contains instructions to compile BlueTruth Raw Data Feed (BRDF).

INSTRUCTIONS
1. Get mongo-cxx-driver. 
Instructions are provided at https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-cxx-driver/wiki/Download-and-Compile-the-Legacy-Driver
- Make sure that scons program is installed,
- Checkout the source code from https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-cxx-driver,
- Compile the code with "scons install" command,
- Move the contents of build/install to /usr/local directory.


GOOD LUCK!


Author: Radoslaw Golebiewski
